                    <span>Excellent history of the Boswell family. Very interesting reading. The authors described many technical aspects of production agriculture in suprising detail considering that they are reporters and not agriculture specialists. <BR>Anyone involved in farm management, agriculture economics, environmental management or agricultural water management will enjoy reading this book.</span>
                  
              
